-content/uploads/2025/01/Los-Angeles-wildfire-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Los-Angeles-wildfire-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Los-Angeles-wildfire-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Los-Angeles-wildfire-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Los-Angeles-wildfire-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.discogs.com/about/news/community-support-los-angeles-fires-2025/?srsltid=AfmBOoqkCIfjy99aA8VLgMv9v_HzQuH-jAXaaKPi-4s28rGKFQmemrNT" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discogs</a>宣布，他们将把 1 月 17 日销售的所有收入捐赠给受洛杉矶山火影响的人们。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶音乐界告诉我们野火的“悲剧性”影响：“这种影响将持续多年”</a></strong></li></ul><p>熊熊大火于上周二（1 月 7 日）首次爆发，已摧毁了数千所房屋，迄今已造成 24 人死亡。据称至少有 16 人失踪，随着寻尸犬在平整的社区进行系统性的网格搜索，当局预计这一数字还会上升。</p><p>失去家园的人包括艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jhene-aiko-and-beyonces-mother-tina-knowles-reveal-theyve-lost-their-homes-in-the-la-wildfires-3827728">Jhené Aiko</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Madlib">Madlib</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Diane-Warren">Diane Warren</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Harry-Mack">Harry Mack</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Iron-Maiden">Iron Maiden</a>吉他手 Adrian Smith、加拿大摇滚乐队 Cola and Ought 的 Tim Darcy、流行二人组 Brijean、 <a href="https://www.instagram.com/share/_wJq_TYdD" target="_blank" rel="noopener">30 Seconds To Mars 吉他手兼音乐总监 Stevie艾洛</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>的母亲<a href="https://www.instagram.com/share/BAGLulZeMf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">蒂娜·诺尔斯</a>。</p><p>包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-cudi">Kid Cudi</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bebe-rexha">Bebe Rexha</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guapdad-4000">Guapdad 4000</a>在内的许多其他人都表示，由于 Pacific Palisades 和 Eaton 大火继续蔓延，他们不得不撤离家园。</p><p>这家音乐收藏家在线市场在其<a href="https://www.discogs.com/about/news/community-support-los-angeles-fires-2025/?srsltid=AfmBOoqkCIfjy99aA8VLgMv9v_HzQuH-jAXaaKPi-4s28rGKFQmemrNT" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方网站</a>上发布了一份声明，透露其 1 月 17 日的所有收入将直接捐赠给<a href="https://musicares.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MusiCares——</a>唱片学院的非营利组织，该组织一直致力于支持艺术家和音乐行业工人疏散、搬迁。正在发生的自然灾害期间的医疗保健、心理健康服务等。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DExrWIvur1v/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C54